Reality TV star, Tobi Bakre, has revealed how his wife stole his heart on their first meeting. The 27-year-old media personality recently welcomed his first child with his wife Anu Bakre. He announced the birth of his son via his Instagram page. According to him, 2021 had a perfect ending because it witnessed the arrival of his son, Abdulmalik Oluwatobi Bakre on December 30. Reminiscing about beautiful memories, Bakre shared a video on his Insta story which shows his wife Anu beautifully doing the ‘legwork’ dance style.   Yemi Alade becomes brand ambassador for ‘Ankara’…     Fashanu, Tboss, attend Adini premiere     Deba Uwadiae releases ‘Imela’   - Advertisement - In the video, the new father disclosed the sight of the person and the ‘legwork’ being done stole his heart away. He noted the event was organised by OAP Toolz and took place on February 9, 2020. According to the actor, if ever asked how he met his wife, he would not stress to respond but play this same video instead. He wrote in pidgin: “When asked how I met my wife, na this video I kuku play. “Na so dem use legwork steal my heart away.”